org.nepas.sbg

Class SBGOutput

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nepas.sbg.SBGOutput

  • public class SBGOutput
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to store data outputted by the SBG device.

    This class is used by SBGComClass read methods to return data read from the connected SBG device.
    See SGB SbgOutput data structure documentation for details!

    Version:
    1.0, 2023-05-10
    Author:
    Alexandre José Tiberti
